name: UnmodifiableMap_unmodifiableMapTest
description: Unit tests for the UnmodifiableMap.unmodifiableMap method.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableMapWithUnmodifiableMap
test_cases.description: Tests that wrapping an unmodifiable map with UnmodifiableMap.unmodifiableMap returns the same instance.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableMapWithModifiableMap
test_cases.description: Tests that wrapping a modifiable map with UnmodifiableMap.unmodifiableMap returns an instance of UnmodifiableMap and is not the same instance as the original map.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableMapWithNullMap
test_cases.description: Tests that passing a null map to UnmodifiableMap.unmodifiableMap throws a NullPointerException.
